title: Orography
body: See Madeira (Orographic Aspects of), II, 314. For this subject, the following articles also offer some interest: Achada, Calhau, North Coast, South Coast, Coasts, Encumeada, Fajã, Geology, Massapez, Quebradas, Salão, and 'Coreographic Dictionary of the Madeira Archipelago' by Father Fernando A. Silva.

Father Fernando A. Silva: Author of the 'Coreographic Dictionary of the Madeira Archipelago'
